      <odd id="aspace_8aa664eb1ff757ea78d008ad5ef5c909">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 37 (YRG 37), Records of associations, institutes, centers, and organizations affiliated with Yale University.</p>  
      </odd>
      <altformavail id="aspace_ce163c4485b4596cd12d1374520795ec">
         <head>Existence and Location of Copies</head>
         <p>The records are available on microfilm (504 frames on 1 reel, 35mm.) from Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library, at cost. Order no. HM171.</p>  
      </altformavail>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_3ffd3e6eda04c16fbf41b0995bd54452" localtype="UseSurrogate">
